{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"cssRule","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSRule","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Własności</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule/cssText\"><code>cssText</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule/parentRule\"><code>parentRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule/parentStyleSheet\"><code>parentStyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule/type\"><code>type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n<p>Obiekt <code>CSSRule</code> reprezentuje pojedynczy arkusz stylu CSS. To może być pojedyncza reguła arkusza stylów CSS. Może być częścią listy <a href=\"pl/DOM/stylesheet\">stylesheet</a> <a href=\"pl/DOM/stylesheet.cssRules\">cssRules</a>.</p>\n<p>Jest tu kilka rodzajów reguł. Wszystkie one dzielą kilka wspólnych własności interfejsu <a href=\"#cssrule\">CSSRule</a> i większość posiada pewne specyficzne własności oraz typy reguł.</p>\n<table class=\"fullwidth-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Typ</th>\n   <th>Interfejs związany z regułą</th>\n   <th>Opis</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>CSSRule.STYLE_RULE</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"#cssstylerule\">CSSStyleRule</a></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>CSSRule.MEDIA_RULE</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"#cssmediarule\">CSSMediaRule</a></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>CSSRule.FONT_FACE_RULE</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"#cssfontfacerule\">CSSFontFaceRule</a></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>CSSRule.PAGE_RULE</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"#csspagerule\">CSSPageRule</a></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>CSSRule.IMPORT_RULE</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"#cssimportrule\">CSSImportRule</a></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>CSSRule.CHARSET_RULE</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"#csscharsetrule\">CSSCharsetRule</a></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>CSSRule.UNKNOWN_RULE</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"#cssunknownrule\">CSSUnknownRule</a></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssrule","title":"CSSRule","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">\n  <a href=\"pl/DOM/cssRule.cssText\">cssText</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  Zwraca tekstową reprezentację reguły, np. \"h1,h2 { font-size: 16pt }\".</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <a href=\"pl/DOM/cssRule.parentRule\">parentRule</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  Zwraca regule zawarta w treści jeśli takowa istnieje, np. regułę stylu znajdującą sie wewnątrz bloku @media.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">\n  <a href=\"pl/DOM/cssRule.parentStyleSheet\">parentStyleSheet</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  Zwraca obiekt <a href=\"pl/DOM/stylesheet\">stylesheet</a>, którego reguła jest częścią.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect4\">\n  <a href=\"pl/DOM/cssRule.type\">type</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  Zwraca typ reguły, np. <code>CSSRule.CHARSET_RULE</code> lub <code>CSSRule.IMPORT_RULE</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssstylerule","title":"CSSStyleRule","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect5\">\n  <a href=\"pl/DOM/cssRule.selectorText\">selectorText</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  Pobiera/ustawia tekstową reprezentację selektora dla reguły, np.: \"h1,h2\".</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect6\">\n  <a href=\"pl/DOM/cssRule.style\">style</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  Zwraca obiekt <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSStyleDeclaration\" rel=\" noopener\">CSSStyleDeclaration</a> dla reguły <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-CSS2-19980512/syndata.html#block\" rel=\" noopener\">deklaracji bloku</a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssstylerule_2","title":"CSSStyleRule","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssmediarule","title":"CSSMediaRule","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssfontfacerule","title":"CSSFontFaceRule","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"csspagerule","title":"CSSPageRule","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssimportrule","title":"CSSImportRule","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"csscharsetrule","title":"CSSCharsetRule","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssunknownrule","title":"CSSUnknownRule","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSRule\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 CSS: CSSRule</a></p>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Obiekt CSSRule reprezentuje pojedynczy arkusz stylu CSS. To może być pojedyncza reguła arkusza stylów CSS. Może być częścią listy stylesheet cssRules.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSRule","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"CSSRule","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CssRule","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CSSRule","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSSRule","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSSRule","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/cssrule","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/cssrule/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSRule","title":"cssRule"}],"pageTitle":"cssRule - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}